ηy ! Y 1 ! X0 ! X1) in the model depicted in Figure A1. These
indirect paths from Figure A1 translate to direct paths in the linear
cross-lagged panel model with T ¼ 4 measurement waves as depicted
in Figure 5. The same argument holds true for the directed edge
from ηx to the insulin levels Y1.
